Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
      • Customer
  • public class Customer
extends Person
    Since:
    11/02/2020, 11/01/2020, 10/30/2020

    Class Description: Customer extends from Person class and stores customer information not already inside of Person class: checking and credit accounts.

    Assumptions: 1) Users have everything inside of Person class. 2) Not all users have a checking and/or a credit account .

    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Yulianna Torres, Isaiah Landin, Judith Garcia
